INSERT INTO `testimonials` (`id`, `name`, `role`, `company`, `photo_url`, `rating`, `text`, `status`, `created_at`, `category`) VALUES (2,'ABHISHEK BHARTIYA','','','review-img/1.jpg',5,'With the help of Elevates, I got the opportunity to start my professional journey at Ternate Techsol Private Limited. The program helped me grow from an underconfident fresher into a corporate-ready professional by simplifying business concepts and strengthening my communication and client-handling skills. The real-world guidance and continuous support made a real difference in my confidence and readiness for the role.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(3,'SAMRA ALI','','','review-img/2.jpg',5,'Elevates has refined my consultative approach, helping me understand client needs better, communicate solutions clearly, and build lasting relationships.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(4,'Akansha Tyagi','','','review-img/3.jpg',5,'ELEVATES helped me transition from campus learning to real corporate execution through its Corporate Success Program. The program provided practical exposure, strengthened my professional communication, and prepared me for real client facing responsibilities. With the right guidance and structured Mentoring, I became industry ready and confidently began my professional journey at Alpha1 IT Solutions & Consulting.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(5,'Gulsaz','','','review-img/4.jpg',5,'ELEVATES helped me strengthen the skills that matter most in a professional environment. The program gave me better clarity on how to present my capabilities, communicate with confidence, and handle workplace conversations more effectively. With continuous guidance and feedback, I was able to refine my approach, improve my overall execution, and feel more confident in how I show up professionally. This learning experience played an important role in helping me move forward and secure my opportunity at Alpha1 IT.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(6,'SHUBHAM YADAV','','','review-img/5.jpg',5,'When I became part of ELEVATES Corporate Success Program, I lacked clarity and had little idea how the corporate world worked. The mentors guided me step by step from understanding IT industry dynamics to developing client management skills. Their continuous support and practice sessions gave me the confidence to express myself professionally and perform better in every interaction.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(7,'Neha Kumari','','','review-img/6.jpg',5,'With ELEVATES\' Corporate Success Program, I received the right guidance, practical exposure, and mentoring that helped me understand how the professional world actually works. The Mentoring strengthened my communication skills and gave me the confidence to step into real corporate environments. This journey truly made me industry ready and helped me begin my professional career at Alpha1 IT Solutions & Consulting.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(8,'RUDRAKSH BOHRA','','','review-img/7.jpg',5,'When I joined Elevates, I was a fresher trying to find my footing in the industry. The personalized guidance and mentorship I received were crucial in preparing me for real-world challenges. Elevates helped me develop relevant skills and gave me the confidence to navigate the job market successfully. I\'m grateful for the practical, focused coaching that made all the difference in launching my career.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(9,'MONIS KHAN','','','review-img/9.jpg',5,'Before Elevates, I struggled to communicate my ideas clearly during client meetings. Their program helped me sharpen my communication, manage clients more effectively, and close bigger deals with confidence.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(10,'KARAN TICKOO','','','review-img/10.jpg',5,'Before joining Elevates program, I wasn\'t able to realise my real potential. Today I am aware of my real strengths and I feel more confident. This Program was a turning point in my journey. It didn\'t just sharpen my understanding of professional concepts- it reshaped how I see myself. ▸ I\'ve developed a confident, growth-oriented mindset. ▸ I now approach challenges with clarity and emotional intelligence. ▸ I\'ve discovered a career path that aligns with my strengths and aspirations. This wasn\'t just a learning experience, it was a transformation. Grateful to the mentors and community that made it possible.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(11,'PARVESH KUMAR','','','review-img/11.jpg',5,'When I started my journey with Elevates, I didn\'t expect it to change so much for me. It wasn\'t just about learning new skills, it was about finding my voice again. Today, I feel more confident speaking, connecting with people, and handling conversations with ease. The best part? It all happened through small, simple steps that made a real difference. Grateful to the Elevates team for helping me grow, both personally and professionally.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(12,'DURGA SARAN','','','review-img/12.jpg',5,'My experience with Elevates has been incredibly rewarding. Their guidance during my interview preparation helped me gain the confidence and clarity I needed. The mock sessions were a game changer; they helped me identify weak areas, refine my responses, and improve my communication skills. I appreciate the personalized support from the mentors who understood my goals and guided me every step of the way. With their help, I enhanced my skills and achieved a 60% salary increment in my new role. A big thank you to the entire ELEVATES team for helping me grow and believe in my potential. This journey wouldn\'t have been the same without you.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(13,'Twinkle Bagchi','','','review-img/13.jpg',5,'This program was instrumental in my career growth, providing me with the tools and expertise to take on more challenging roles and responsibilities.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(14,'VIVEK THAKUR','','','review-img/14.jpg',5,'Looking back at my journey, learning with ELEVATES has been one of the most impactful decisions in my career. Their mock sessions and interview preparation helped me sharpen my skills and gain real clarity about my professional direction. Their encouragement built my confidence and helped me take practical steps toward meaningful growth. With ELEVATES support, I not only enhanced my skills but also secured an 80% salary hike in my new role. I\'m genuinely grateful to the team for guiding me toward this milestone with clarity and confidence.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(15,'BHAVIT DAVE','','','review-img/8.jpg',5,'Our association with ELEVATES helped us onboard candidates who are confident, communicative, and truly corporate-ready. Their structured mentoring and strong focus on professional mindset clearly reflect in how candidates adapt, collaborate, and perform from day one. ELEVATES builds talent that aligns well with real industry expectations.','published','2026-03-16 09:12:33','b2c'),(16,'RAHUL MATHUR','Director','Emicron Techsolutions Pvt Ltd','review-img/testimonial_1774863511_9560.jpg',5,'Partnering with Elevates has been one of our best business decisions. Their program not only enhanced our team\'s skills but also reshaped how we build trust with customers- driving stronger relationships, greater loyalty, and improved retention and revenue. Elevates also played a pivotal role in upskilling our team, equipping them with the confidence and tools to lead with empathy, clarity and impact. This investment in our people has directly contributed to higher employee engagement and talent retention. Elevates isn\'t just a program-it\'s a game changer.','published','2026-03-30 09:06:54','b2b'),(17,'ABHINAY PRATAP','','','review-img/testimonial_1774863495_3954.jpg',5,'What stood out to me about ELEVATES was how practical and relevant it felt to my work. The mentors played a key role in helping me navigate real client handling situations, clear long standing doubts, and approach challenges with better judgment.\r\nThis made it easier to handle my work with more clarity and confidence, and be more mindful in my approach.','published','2026-03-30 09:18:40','b2c'),(18,'SHALINI JOSHI','Vice President','Alpha1 IT Solutions & Consulting','review-img/testimonial_1774863479_8024.jpg',5,'Our association with ELEVATES helped us onboard candidates who are confident, communicative, and truly corporate-ready. Their structured mentoring and strong focus on professional mindset clearly reflect in how candidates adapt, collaborate, and perform from day one.\r\nELEVATES builds talent that aligns well with real industry expectations.','published','2026-03-30 09:26:22','b2b'),(19,'AMIT POPLI','Director','Ternate Techsol Private Limited','review-img/testimonial_1774863433_7026.jpg',5,'We greatly value our association with ELEVATES Corporate Success Program. Their structured approach and mentorship have enabled us to build a dynamic team of young professionals who are well-prepared for sales roles. By strengthening their capabilities in lead generation, client handling and value-based selling, ELEVATES has directly contributed to improving our business outcomes.','published','2026-03-30 09:33:46','b2b'),(20,'Mani Sinha','','','review-img/mani-sinha.png',5,'From confidence building to interview preparation, ELEVATES provided the guidance and support I needed to navigate my layoff and move forward with confidence.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:19','b2c'),(21,'Prashant Kumar','','','review-img/prashant-kumar.png',5,'Through ELEVATES, I developed stronger communication, public speaking, and leadership skills that transformed the way I interact with customers and teams.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2c'),(22,'Debashish Maji','','','review-img/debashish-maji.png',5,'ELEVATES has helped our team strengthen communication, enhance client interactions, and approach every opportunity with greater confidence and professionalism.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2b'),(23,'Rakesh Pandey','','','review-img/rakesh-pandey.png',5,'ELEVATES mentorship has played a valuable role in developing professionals who think with clarity, communicate effectively, and deliver greater value to customers.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2b'),(24,'Shikhar Shukla','','','',5,'What stands out about ELEVATES is its practical approach to professional development. The impact is reflected in the confidence, mindset, and execution of our team.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2b'),(25,'Tarika Nigam','','','review-img/tarika.png',5,'ELEVATES helped me strengthen my communication, build confidence, and approach my professional journey with greater clarity and purpose.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2c'),(26,'Shubham Mer','','NetApp','review-img/shubham-mer.png',5,'ELEVATES helped me sharpen my professional communication and approach every business conversation with greater clarity and purpose.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2c'),(27,'Priyanka Tisoria','','','review-img/priyanka-tisoria.png',5,'The mentorship at ELEVATES enhanced my confidence, communication, and ability to build lasting relationships with customers.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2c'),(28,'Mayank Bhatia','','','review-img/mayank-bhatia.png',5,'ELEVATES helped me look beyond products and focus on delivering meaningful business value through every customer interaction.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2c'),(29,'Ravi Singh','','','review-img/ravi-singh.png',5,'The practical insights from ELEVATES helped me build confidence, improve client conversations, and strengthen my professional approach.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2c'),(30,'Subhadip','','','review-img/subhadip.png',5,'ELEVATES gave me a broader business perspective, enabling me to approach customer conversations with greater confidence and strategic thinking.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2c'),(31,'Shubham Pandey','','','review-img/shubham-pandey.png',5,'The mentorship at ELEVATES strengthened my consultative approach, helping me build stronger customer relationships and communicate value more effectively.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2c'),(32,'Prikshit Awasthi','','','review-img/prikshit.png',5,'ELEVATES helped me communicate technical solutions with greater clarity and confidence, making every customer interaction more impactful.','published','2026-06-25 17:53:20','b2c');
